      "representation": "view",
      "value": "<div class=\"contentLayout2\">\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544641289/RenderMan_Solaris_LightFilters_Render.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433087859&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544641289/RenderMan_Solaris_LightFilters_Render.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433087859&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544641336\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderMan_Solaris_LightFilters_Render.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544641289\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"7\" data-media-id=\"73dcf4cf-7001-4601-8c3d-4752261c6320\" data-media-type=\"file\"></span><br/><br/><br/><span class=\"legacy-color-text-default\">Light Filters are used to manipulate lighting results. In the real world, stencils and gels often achieve this by changing the color, quality, and amount of light in a shot. RenderMan's light filters are a powerful and flexible way to do the same (and even more) in lighting your scenes. </span></p><p><span class=\"legacy-color-text-default\">Working with Light Filters in Solaris is simple and will instantly transform your lights and lighting!</span></p><hr/><p>To add a light filter simply add one of the dedicated LOP node to create the corresponding USD light filter primitive.</p><div class=\"confluence-information-macro confluence-information-macro-information conf-macro output-block\" data-hasbody=\"true\" data-macro-id=\"de8a6518-546e-400c-9974-8b52ddc2f7ed\" data-macro-name=\"info\"><span class=\"aui-icon aui-icon-small aui-iconfont-info confluence-information-macro-icon\"> </span><div class=\"confluence-information-macro-body\"><p>The previous <em>PxrLightFilter</em> LOP, while still working, is deprecated.</p></div></div><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"lightFilterLOPs.png\" width=\"964\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544641289/lightFilterLOPs.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1763060755923&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=964&amp;height=512\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544641289/lightFilterLOPs.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1763060755923&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"512\" data-width=\"964\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"665550881\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"lightFilterLOPs.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544641289\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"7\" data-media-id=\"421bab17-1ca0-41b9-9bdd-514932304418\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544641289/lightFilterLOPs.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1763060755923&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=964&amp;height=512 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544641289/lightFilterLOPs.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1763060755923&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=964&amp;height=512 1x\"></span><p /><p>Then assign it to a light using one of the following methods:</p><ul><li><p>Use a PxrAssign LOP (or the PxrAssignLightFilter alias). You can use a single PxrAssign LOP to assign multiple light filters to multiple lights.</p></li><li><p>Use a Light Edit LOP and fill the <em>Light Filters</em> parameter on the <em>Base Properties</em> tab</p></li><li><p>Plase a Light Edit LOP after the light filter LOP and fill the <em>Light Filters</em> parameter on the <em>Base Properties</em> tab</p></li></ul><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"assignLighFilter.png\" width=\"916\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544641289/assignLighFilter.png?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1763068324744&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=916&amp;height=262\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544641289/assignLighFilter.png?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1763068324744&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"262\" data-width=\"916\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"663814282\" data-linked-resource-version=\"2\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"assignLighFilter.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544641289\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"7\" data-media-id=\"5cd88784-6224-425a-a992-f44f192c3b9c\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544641289/assignLighFilter.png?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1763068324744&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=916&amp;height=262 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544641289/assignLighFilter.png?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1763068324744&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=916&amp;height=262 1x\"></span><p>If the assignment was properly done, in the Scene Graph, on the light primitive, the light filter primitive should be listed on the light:filters attribute.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"lightFilterAssgined.png\" width=\"1118\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544641289/lightFilterAssgined.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1763060771941&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1118&amp;height=248\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544641289/lightFilterAssgined.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1763060771941&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"265\" data-width=\"1190\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"663519410\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"lightFilterAssgined.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544641289\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"7\" data-media-id=\"e86f653e-47cf-435b-997b-9760a897125a\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544641289/lightFilterAssgined.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1763060771941&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1190&amp;height=265 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544641289/lightFilterAssgined.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1763060771941&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1118&amp;height=248 1x\"></span><p>To parent a light filter to a light (as shown above in the Scene Graph), simply set the <em>Primitive Path</em> parameter on the light filter LOP with the proper path (e.g. ‘/lights/light1/$OS instead of the default '/lightFilters/$OS’).</p><p /><hr/><p><br/></p><p>Example</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"RenderMan_Solaris_LightFilters_Render_2.jpg\" width=\"1389\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544641289/RenderMan_Solaris_LightFilters_Render_2.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433087295&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1389&amp;height=781\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544641289/RenderMan_Solaris_LightFilters_Render_2.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433087295&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"1080\" data-width=\"1920\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544641309\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderMan_Solaris_LightFilters_Render_2.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544641289\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"7\" data-media-id=\"6dbc3ba7-9f19-4bf5-a584-87b7fcf85f8f\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544641289/RenderMan_Solaris_LightFilters_Render_2.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433087295&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1920&amp;height=1080 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544641289/RenderMan_Solaris_LightFilters_Render_2.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433087295&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1389&amp;height=781 1x\"></span></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout two-right-sidebar\" data-layout=\"two-right-sidebar\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-left-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-left\" alt=\"RenderMan_Solaris_LightFilters_Render_3.jpg\" width=\"622\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544641289/RenderMan_Solaris_LightFilters_Render_3.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433087295&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=622&amp;height=349\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544641289/RenderMan_Solaris_LightFilters_Render_3.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433087295&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"1080\" data-width=\"1920\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544641306\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderMan_Solaris_LightFilters_Render_3.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544641289\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"7\" data-media-id=\"42c8ca08-dbc1-4b4d-baa2-6576ae6764a1\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544641289/RenderMan_Solaris_LightFilters_Render_3.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433087295&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1244&amp;height=698 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544641289/RenderMan_Solaris_LightFilters_Render_3.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433087295&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=622&amp;height=349 1x\"></span></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell aside\" data-type=\"aside\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-right-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-right\" alt=\"wings.jpg\" width=\"350\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544641289/wings.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433087295&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=350&amp;height=350\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544641289/wings.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433087295&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"2000\" data-width=\"2000\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544641303\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"wings.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544641289\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"7\" data-media-id=\"e3e6dd4b-d52f-47df-be01-a98331ac8e97\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544641289/wings.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433087295&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=700&amp;height=700 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544641289/wings.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433087295&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=350&amp;height=350 1x\"></span></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<p><br/></p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>"
